INSERT INTO `messages` VALUES (86, 496, 481, 409, '2400 gameplay', 'Thea1ien', '2005-09-19 14:18:56', 0, 'SUBJ: 2400 gameplay                    FROM: Thea1ien    09/19/2005 S# 496\nI dont think it will work for the 2400 users at all, at least not right now.\nThere is a majoy difference noticed for the 2400 baud users when they try to play. Normally after the game has loaded and is waiting for the other person to finish loading, you can send and chat with others in the lobby you are in. But for a 2400 user, after the game is loaded, not only are you waiting for the other player, but the chat no longer works. However during my testing, it seems the 2400 user is still active on Qlink, as the server never drops them due to a timeout or anything...till I reboot that system...\n\nSo 2400 baud users are getting stuck in limbo somehow...\n ');
