INSERT INTO `messages` VALUES (110, 523, 518, 409, 'Yes!', 'QGUIDE ob', '2005-09-30 16:24:12', 0, 'SUBJ: Yes!                             FROM: QGUIDE ob   09/30/2005 S# 523\nI''m seeking people who are willing to fill the positions of QGUIDES, QTENDS, FORUM OPS, LIBRARY MAINT, ACTIVITIES, etc!  We ask that you commit to at least 4-6 months if you get something started. (You are not limited to that, but we want to keep the ball rolling once something is started)\n\nPiority will be given to those wishing to fill positions for existing sections, however, all ideas and volunteer are wanted and welcome.\n\nIf you have an idea for something, or are willing to fill a position please email jeff@jer333.com with the details of what you have in mind.\n\nPlease keep in mind that there is an objective to keep this service ''family friendly''\n\nThanks for asking!\nJeff\nQGUIDE ob\n\n ');
